#### DLL List — Detecting Unlisted DLLs

```bash
python vol.py -f WS-FIN-047.mem windows.dlllist --pid 1492
```

Cross-referenced against `windows.ldrmodules` to detect hidden/unlinked DLLs:

```bash
python vol.py -f WS-FIN-047.mem windows.ldrmodules --pid 1492
```

```
Base        InLoad  InInit  InMem  MappedPath
----------  ------  ------  -----  -------------------------
0x1d0000    False   False   True   [NO PATH — anonymous mapping]
```

> **`InLoad: False, InMem: True`** confirms the DLL is loaded in memory but deliberately unlinked from the PEB loader list — a hallmark of Cobalt Strike's reflective loader.

