## Containment Actions Taken

1. Isolated `WS-FIN-047` at the switch port level immediately
2. Deleted malicious scheduled task from all endpoints via CrowdStrike RTR
3. Blocked C2 IP `94.102.49.190` at perimeter firewall and web proxy
4. Forced password reset for `asingh` and reviewed all activity over 11-day dwell window
5. Hunted for same Cobalt Strike watermark across all endpoints via memory scanning
6. Submitted beacon PE to VirusTotal and internal threat intel platform

