## Recommendations

| Finding | Recommendation |
|---------|---------------|
| Excel spawning PowerShell undetected | Enable ASR rule: Block Office apps from creating child processes |
| Reflective injection into spoolsv.exe | Deploy memory scanning (CrowdStrike Falcon Insight — AMSI integration) |
| 11-day dwell before detection | Tune EDR for anomalous outbound from print spooler processes |
| No email attachment sandboxing | Implement sandboxed detonation for all .xlsm/.xlsb attachments |
| Scheduled task persistence undetected | Alert on scheduled tasks with PowerShell IEX in arguments |

